{"type": "article", "id": 43354, "title": "Coach 男士香水出炉，以及，Balenciaga 又出个毛绒玩具系列 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-25T03:15:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 20076, "name": "monkey time"}, {"id": 42648, "name": "China Town"}, {"id": 25221, "name": "VF"}, {"id": 36433, "name": "J.C Penney"}, {"id": 14669, "name": "Chiara Ferragni"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201707251015243i6jJbKwPndxUM1V.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/markets/vf-corp-adds-40m-accelerate-growth-plans-steve-rendle-eric-wiseman-10951100/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Vans 母公司第二季度利润大涨</strong></a> | 在截止至 6 月 30 日的三个月内，Vans 母公司、VF 集团销售额同比增长 1.7% 至 23.6 亿美元，净利润大涨 115% 至 1.09 亿美元。VF 集团对未来充满信心，并打算投资 4000 万美元以提振目前的势头，加速 2018 业绩增长。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/chiara-ferragni-opens-first-ever-store-in-milan/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>时尚博主 Chiara Ferragni 将在米兰开首家同名旗舰店</strong></a> | 这家店位于米兰的 via Capelli，占地 120 平米，与 Christian Louboutin 和 Gdcs 相邻。据称，<a href=\"http://www.chiaraferragnicollection.com/uk_en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chiara Ferragni</a> 品牌在去年一年营收超过了 2000 万美元，现在，该品牌在实体店和电商平台上共有 300 多个销售点。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/penneys-names-jeffrey-davis-10951357/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国百货连锁 J.C Penney 任命新的 CFO </strong></a>| Jeffrey Davis 将接替 Andrew Drexler，出任 J.C Penney 的 CFO。 他的主要目标将包括进一步确定盈利增长的机遇，优化定价，管理库存并降低债务。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>CALVIN KLEIN 为 Raf Simons 上任以来的首个作品，2017 年秋季系列拍摄了 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/raf-simons-calvin-klein-205w39nyc-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">205W39NYC 形象广告</a>，广告请来了资深摄影师 Willy Vanderperre 操刀，22 位模特儿共同演绎，再现了美式经典户外风格。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105309lxa8viqkAn4bN3Qe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105314aFAdwhtS5Y6UPvkl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251053071DVZHT93BNKaIJmW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105307LpUo0WGXvkHjy7bd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105307LU7fpASNdTXKa63k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105308MApZYyNia2ePlnwH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105308qfIlBvMbuHVXrEdU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105308M79OlxPiS510yqhR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105308vbORJMWiqS5ZjIUV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105308GCXgmvjwrt4c3z5U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105322cZgMSbhdsLQPCJox.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105322fntAre98a1gu4bZ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-07-21/coach-mens-fragrance/topics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coach 的第一款男士香水</a>将于 9 月 13 日在日本正式发售。这款香水请来了 James Franco 做广告，60 ml 装的售价为 8500 日元，100 ml 的 11100 日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105254EUI9tnb1aZTzhRjJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.719697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105246XhVTNwezIxELHl62.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105246Y0TcF7Hhe1Zpy8O3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>近些年还挺火的纽约新晋街牌 China Town，一直以来都以玩味十足的设计吸引眼球。在品牌最新的 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/chinatown-markets-summer-school-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Summer School 系列中</a>，就参照了美国高中的 YEAR BOOK，为模特拍大头照并留下了一句格言，还挺有趣的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105113eZ706NwzobTCSirs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105110XBkY2nfT76QtwxH8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105110ZiGal4xyWSMCF5K7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105111uvDGqZHfC6g5spBT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105110tLfhBjTG6Yqa2uPr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105112UDOM4e6LrNozbXQs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105112EiCVa5jrSg31M2Rh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105112rpiZUd8HB6tTJ5Vh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105112LuIfKF6Zn90EAXD2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>PUMA <a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/puma-womens-basket-platform-strap/\" rel=\"nofollow\">全新 Basket Platform Strap 鞋款</a>，带来了魔术贴的设计，共有黑、白、棕三色可选。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105130Yzkc5lXjpZL1uGKd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105139iS5KcVfGDsBIm3e7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105139W7o1XUkaCu8lsSdZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105139zw1KnG6b5LutOepv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105140Yekf1WzcuVLbdI6w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105140dOY6eBW7AD2Kmpux.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251051401zLA0Vq5OfokMmlr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251051406Mdh1EkD2erWuAcZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105141Lgvid9Hz678AJICX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105141PgfrdlpqTIcZAnSY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/pleasures-monkey-time-2017-spring-summer-capsule\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国街头品牌 Pleasures 联手日本潮牌 Monkey Time，带来了 2017 夏季最新联名系列</a>，主打的是 90 年代怀旧印花风。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105201K0mV18FwXkRTedJj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052018cyPOZTBXRK6I9br.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105201PCa1VEJwvlSX4dHI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105202ujeNbnphOGgdc9k7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105202bRM87gXCfGOhyBLA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052020fv7PU6Zs4HM5nL3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105203OUN2Rp16bHGTa9wY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105203sOh5X21vHMncliIG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052030ogc28v3krVUMQZL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052048vbdyK6ricL1Czxf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052033IjBMAevEkYPKFwo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052040lf93bNtnhoaiPHq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105204ixZpfQszCy4uVIBY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105205mI8Ozvkdjw0tDRs9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105205mdiuxWXj0rOHJMPe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105205HQ8gtS5fPaZ1ILFM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>继天价购物袋、铅笔之后，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/07/24/balenciaga-stuffed-animals/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga 又推出了一个毛绒填充玩具系列</a>。该系列包括穿着 Balenciaga 衣服的长颈鹿、北极熊、猴子、企鹅等，售价在 145 美元至 190 美元不等，现已于巴黎 colette 发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105223cvW9p43ngjX0My1x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170725105223o0NOhZAsTx49mP8Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052307ldbfA9YPEM6t2OC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707251052305b8oiCxKsSLvdW0u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/raf-simons-calvin-klein-205w39nyc-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}